description: When you visit Gopāl's Crêperie, don't expect to get your standard French crêpes. Gopāl's sports an entirely gluten-free and vegetarian menu, and their delicious handmade crepes are made from a blend of non-wheat flours and garbanzo beans that perfectly support both sweet and savory fillings. Don't miss their handmade vegan sorbets either!Gopāl's Crêperie is also dedicated to supporting Kauai's local organic farmers!
name: Gopāl's Crêperie
